snippet.title: JOHNNY DEPP v Amber Heard (The Sun) | Johnny Depp WITNESS Statement (2 of 3) Full Readthrough
snippet.description:
This video Johnny Depp v Amber Heard is a full readthrough of Johnny Depps second witness statement from the UK trial. The first Johnny Depp statment is not public.

This is the first of multiple videos to be released every 2-3 days, each covering another witness statement from the Johnny Depp v Amber Heard (The Sun) trial in the UK.

Big thanks to Les for doing the voice over for each female witness.
